### Get All Users ###

# GET to fetch all users
GET http://localhost:3333/users HTTP/1.1

### Get Users - Pagination ###

# GET to fetch users with pagination (page 1, default limit)
GET http://localhost:3333/users?page=1 HTTP/1.1

###

# GET to fetch users with pagination (page 2, limit 5)
GET http://localhost:3333/users?page=2&limit=5 HTTP/1.1

###

# GET to fetch users with pagination (page 1, limit 10)
GET http://localhost:3333/users?page=1&limit=10 HTTP/1.1

### Get Users - Search ###

# GET to search users by first name
GET http://localhost:3333/users?search=jo√£o HTTP/1.1

###

# GET to search users (case insensitive)
GET http://localhost:3333/users?search=maria HTTP/1.1

###

# GET to search users with pagination
GET http://localhost:3333/users?search=silva&page=1&limit=5 HTTP/1.1

### Get Users - Ordering ###

# GET to fetch users ordered by first_name
GET http://localhost:3333/users?orderBy=first_name HTTP/1.1

###

# GET to fetch users ordered by id
GET http://localhost:3333/users?orderBy=id HTTP/1.1

###

# GET to search and order users
GET http://localhost:3333/users?search=santos&orderBy=first_name HTTP/1.1

### Get Users - Combined Filters ###

# GET with search, order and pagination
GET http://localhost:3333/users?search=silva&orderBy=first_name&page=1&limit=3 HTTP/1.1
